<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Sofie Richie is the face of Italian sportswear brand, Kappa, and Los Angeles-founded leisurewear brand, Juicy Couture's debut capsule collection. </p>

<p>The 22-year-old daughter of Lionel Richie brings an exciting energy to the collaboration's campaign, photographed by Amber Asal.</p>

<p>And it's no surprise, as she's been lending her beauty and personality to of-the-moment label's for some time. In the last year, she's starred in advertisements for Rolla's, Missguided and Frankies Bikinis to name a few.</p>

